<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-01 01:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5540 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-DRAFT-ART-2NDLD-W     07-01 1009
</HEADER>
