<DOCNO> NYT19990701.0075 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-01 10:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5738 &Cx1f; tad-z
r p &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV04-C     07-01 0598
