<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV04-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: GAUGE THE EBBING POLITICAL TIDE
 &HT;    Moving in (k) commentary and (p) political categories for
release Sunday, July 4.
