BILL BRADLEY'S BIG IDEA As a Democratic presidential candidate,
Bill Bradley has a big idea : Himself. So far it's working pretty
well. And that's been good for him, because lately, on the early
campaign trail, he has been remarkably abstract about any other
ideas he might have for making America great. By Melinda
Henneberger. From The New York Times Magazine. Full-length (4,400
words) + edited article available.
