   TRAVEL-COOPERSTOWN (Cooperstown, N.Y.) _ Cooperstown is gearing
up for perhaps the more spectacular induction weekend ever: George
Brett, Robin Yount and Nolan Ryan. Photos, map. Has sidebar in
separate file slugged Travel-coopside. By JOE POSNANSKI. 1,800
words. Story will move in the ``l'' category.
