<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-01 13:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5957 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CHILDCARE-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      07-01 1640
