   FILM-LOLA &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Agile and light on its feet, ``Run Lola Run'' will be
considered an art movie only because it's in German and with
subtitles. Otherwise, its sleekness, speediness and carefully
accessorized techno song score would make it a much bigger deal
than it may turn out to be. Too bad, because its primary-colored
buoyancy will make it one of the most imitated pictures around. By
ELVIS MITCHELL. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
