   VIDEOPOKER _ GONZALES, La. _ The Cajun Circus Casino was among
video poker outlets across Louisana planning ``blackout'' parties
Wednesday night after a federal judge denied appeals to keep open
video poker operations in counties that voted out the gaming in a
referendum a year ago. (Konigsmark, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
