   FREE-PC (Los Angeles) _ Coming now: the free personal computer.
With computer prices falling and competition rising for services
such as Internet access and search engines, companies are flocking
to give consumers free computers in exchange for long-term Internet
service contracts. In recent days Internet giants such as America
Online, Microsoft's MSN Internet Access and Prodigy have flooded
