<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-01 20:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6515 &Cx1f; tta-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NY-SUV-825(2TAKES)-NY     07-01 0862
