 &QL; 
CAMPAIGN-LOOPHOLE (Washington) _ The Republican Party has sent a
letter to GOP presidential candidates suggesting the party intends
to exploit the same ``soft money'' loophole in 2000 that
contributed to the highly-publicized campaign-finance abuses of
1996, The Arizona Republic has learned. In the June 18 letter, the
Republican National Committee told all of the Republican
